description: EAS AdvantEDGE Carb Control Protein Shakes are designed to support your goals of getting lean and toned by giving you the protein you want, without the stuff you don’t. Each shake includes 17 grams of high-quality protein to nourish muscles and help manage hunger with only 100 calories. Our shakes offer an excellent source of antioxidant vitamins C & E to support immunity as well as B-vitamins for energy and protein metabolism. There will always be challenges when you are working to get lean and toned and you need an easy choice when there are obstacles. Control what you can with AdvantEDGE Carb Control.
title: EAS® AdvantEDGE® Carb Control™ Protein Shake - Dark Chocolate - 11oz/4ct

bullets: Support your goals to get lean and toned with this convenient, ready-to-drink protein shake
17 grams of high-quality protein to nourish muscles and help manage hunger
100 calories per serving, 5 grams or less of carbohydrates and no sugar
Excellent source of antioxidant vitamins C and E to support immunity
Each shake includes B vitamins to convert carbs, protein and fat into useful energy

description: Push your performance with EAS Myoplex Original Ready-to-Drink Protein Shakes. One shake provides you with 42 grams of protein and 8.75 grams of naturally occurring BCAAs to aid in muscle recovery. Each serving is an excellent source of eight B-vitamins for energy and protein metabolism as well as antioxidant vitamins C and E and Selenium for immune support. No matter your goal, athletic ability or body type, we have a proven legacy of trusted, innovative sports nutrition products designed especially for you.
title: EAS® Myoplex Original Protein Shake - Chocolate Fudge - 4ct

bullets: BUILD MUSCLE: One packet of EAS Myoplex Original Protein Powder provides 42 grams of high quality protein to help you build muscle and recover quickly
RECOVER: Each serving of protein powder delivers 8.75 grams of BCAAs to stimulate protein synthesis and help repair muscle damage
HIGH-QUALITY: NSF tested
USE: Consume within 30 minutes after strenuous exercise to help repair and rebuild muscles. Also available as a ready-to-drink protein shake.
